---
import ContactButton from "../components/ContactButton.astro"
---

<header
  class='bg-[url(/images/paisaje.jpg)] bg-cover lg:h-screen'
>
  <nav
    class='flex top-0 w-full px-6 py-4 md:z-50 md:fixed md:backdrop-blur-md md:font-semibold items-center md:px-12 max-md:flex-col md:flex-row sm:justify-center md:justify-between text-center bg-transparent md:py-4 text-white justify-items-center lg:text-lg'
  >
    <div class='flex max-md:flex-col text-white'>
      <img
        class='object-scale-down h-14 md:pr-8'
        src='/images/logo.png'
        alt='Landak'
      />
    </div>
    <ul class='flex max-md:flex-col space-x-3 lg:space-x-8 items-center'>
      <li class='hover:text-[#04303b] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out'><a href='/'>Inicio</a></li>
      <li class='hover:text-[#04303b] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out'><a href='#services'>Productos</a></li>
      <li class='hover:text-[#04303b] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out'><a href='#solutions'>Nosotros</a></li>
    </ul>
    <ContactButton />
  </nav>
  <div
    class='grid grid-col md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center text-white h-full align-middle '
  >
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4 md:ps-32 text-center md:text-start">
    <h1
      class='text-4xl md:text-6xl text-principal/90 font-semibold text-[#82c75c]'
    >
      Finca Landak
    </h1>

    <p class='text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#82c75c]'>Agrecología Integral</p>

    <p class='text-wrap:pretty text-sm md:text-xl md:max-w-xl'>
      Somos Apiario Landak, un emprendimiento familiar vinculado a la comunidad
      étnica del Consejo Comunitario Afro Vallecito. Nuestra miel orgánica cruda
      es producida directamente en las montañas del municipio PEDET Pradera, en
      el Cauca, entre los 1.500 y 1.800 msnm.
    </p>

    <div class='flex flex-col gap-2 md:gap-4 md:pt-12 sm:flex-row pb-2 md:pb-0'>
      <a
        href='#services'
        class='rounded-sm px-4 py-3 text-sm text-center font-normal bg-transparent border hover:border-[#82c75c] hover:bg-[#82c75c] border-white animation: transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out'
        >Explora nuestros servicios</a
      >
      <a
        href='#contact'
        class='rounded-sm px-4 py-3 text-sm text-center font-normal border hover:border-[#82c75c] hover:bg-[#82c75c] animation: transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out'
        >Contacta con Nosotros</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</header>
